text: Lauren Le Vine After the shocking flub that was La La Land mistakenly being awarded best picture instead of Moonlight , the show—or rather, the party—still had to go on. From Janelle Monáe living it up to Matt Damon and Jimmy Kimmel continuing their feud, see the most amusing, delightful, and selfie-inception ( Elizabeth Banks and Reese Witherspoon ) moments from the Vanity Fair Oscar party right here.
